[
  {
    "key": "4f04db970fac7c0873f7bf66dcd1d220175ab4cc9f3d5fda0b26e99144faf795",
    "original": "A wandering hedge knight, you were a veteran of jousting and sparring tournaments. You were also a veteran of victory. Tis a scary thought for many, but if it were anything at all that turned your eye toward mercenary work it was boredom. Outwardly you state it is for the coin, but a part of you knows it's also for the company.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "bro.getBackground().m.RawDescription = \"A wandering hedge knight, you were a veteran of jousting and sparring tournaments. You were also a veteran of victory. Tis a scary thought for many, but if it were anything at all that turned your eye toward mercenary work it was boredom. Outwardly you state it is for the coin, but a part of you knows it's also for the company.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "ffb4e008d90ec8db14582dbfffe6a7b8f2eab0b7f698f63aec25b0bdeeafbb53",
    "original": "Lone Wolf",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "this.m.Name = \"Lone Wolf\""
  },
  {
    "key": "e204bf67cb5d0173d4cfb77675a4533b94c3aa198dd7351239a82ceef1f6f47e",
    "original": "[p=c][img]gfx/ui/events/event_35.png[/img][/p][p]You've been traveling alone for a long time, taking part in tourneys and sparring with young nobles. A hedge knight tall as a tree, you never needed anybody for long. Is it true still?\n\n[color=#bcad8c]Lone Wolf:[/color] Start with a single experienced hedge knight and great equipment, but low funds.\n[color=#bcad8c]Elite Few:[/color] Can never have more than 12 men in your roster.\n[color=#bcad8c]Avatar:[/color] If your hedge knight dies, the campaign ends.[/p]",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "this.m.Description = \"[p=c][img]gfx/ui/events/event_35.png[/img][/p][p]You've been traveling alone for a long time, taking part in tourneys and sparring with young nobles. A hedge knight tall as a tree, you never needed anybody for long. Is it true still?\\n\\n[color=#bcad8c]Lone Wolf:[/color] Start with a single experienced hedge knight and great equipment, but low funds.\\n[color=#bcad8c]Elite Few:[/color] Can never have more than 12 men in your roster.\\n[color=#bcad8c]Avatar:[/color] If your hedge knight dies, the campaign ends.[/p]\""
  },
  {
    "key": "d5d2c08f307dc9bdeba06d2fb812b82f7a3b15c1824f52834d1b94ea29bdc10b",
    "original": "the Lone Wolf",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  }
]